---
title: Easy Bacon, Feta & Potato Pie with Filo Pastry & Roasted Broccoli
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie-loaded bacon base that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a light and
flakey filo pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652f66ec3682d11088748fce-84e8bcf3.jpeg
